  "detailed_description": "Now it's all up to you how quiet the city will be...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPolice Transporter Simulator is a sim game in which you have to transport police vehicles (cars, tanks, trucks). It's a well-paid job, so you have to take care of the goods you carry. But beware, no one needs to know what you're doing and where you're going!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features : <br />\r\n- 10 levels that include various types of transport (trucks, cars, tanks)<br />\r\n- Daily Bonus that allow to earn more coins <br />\r\n- Time-based missions that become more and more difficult",
  "about_the_game": "Now it's all up to you how quiet the city will be...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPolice Transporter Simulator is a sim game in which you have to transport police vehicles (cars, tanks, trucks). It's a well-paid job, so you have to take care of the goods you carry. But beware, no one needs to know what you're doing and where you're going!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Features : <br />\r\n- 10 levels that include various types of transport (trucks, cars, tanks)<br />\r\n- Daily Bonus that allow to earn more coins <br />\r\n- Time-based missions that become more and more difficult",
